Re: SCP-5380: -1


01 Sep 2020 19:29






You're probably thinking of 251 or 2028 but there effects are pretty different from this one. 251 creates scenes of violence in the snow globe. 2028 captures people's nightmares inside it, and it causes a reality restructuring event that replicates the nightmare in the real world if it's broken. Neither of them change the weather when there shaken. I think the mother-son relationship examined in 5380 helps make it unique.







